{"tid":1072614,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"求救lan線上網成日斷，遠端主機停止接收訊息","createTime":"2019-03-22T06:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T16:58:42.000Z","uid":56439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3ccd649dcae2e9755865cc87eaf3c3182d74bba7","tid":1072614,"uid":56439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T06:34:38.000Z","msg":"打打下機會自己斷可以幾秒至十幾秒會自己連番，什至唔識連番<br />\n試過2個情況都斷<br />\n1.modem 直插lan線入電腦（而家用緊）<br />\n2.modem入router lantop出<br />\n<br />\n但wifi冇野<br />\n<br />\n試過方法<br />\n1.換router<br />\n2.換左寬頻 由香港寬頻1000mb轉做pccw1000mb<br />\n3.試過唔同lan線 都係cat6<br />\n4.裝過lan driver <br />\n都唔得<br />\n<br />\n究竟咩問題，好煩躁阿"},{"pid":"90f6b8867a02febeb19006a01b567aa49af2e887","tid":1072614,"uid":227089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T08:04:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"624b52bba4ce699a29162059ce19ce6b3cc6616b","tid":1072614,"uid":56439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T16:58:42.000Z","msg":"求救"}]}